---
title: Caribbean Chicken & Coconut Rice with Caramelised Pineapple Salsa
description: Caribbean spice is such a party for your mouth that we had to step up every element of this lively dish, from the
pineapple salsa to the coconut-spinach rice. If you like things mild, just leave out the chilli – the salsa is already
packed with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-chicken-with-coconut-rice-87b6439c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/caribbean-chicken-with-coconut-rice-60dd291cb40df24f87741b24-8c582d5c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/caribbean-chicken-and-coconut-rice-60dd291cb40df24f87741b24
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Caribbean
author: HelloFresh
